3. **In your relationships**: Practice one act of reciprocal duty this week—repair harm, share knowledge, listen to a marginalized voice without fixing. *Notice how it changes your sense of agency.*  

> **We do not inherit the Earth from our ancestors; we borrow it from our children.**  
> This framework is a promise to those children: *We will learn to live within the bounds of life—or we will not live at all.*  
