#### **3. Revise Dynamic Knowledge (Pillar 3): Absent Referent Literacy as Core Competency**  
> **Current Pillar 3**: Dynamic Knowledge (includes epistemic humility, knowledge pluralism)  
> **Adams’ Revision**: ***Dynamic Knowledge & Absent Referent Literacy***  
