## Matthew Scully's Response to the Earth Stewardship Framework (ESF) v0.8:  
A Stewardship-and-Mercy Critique Rooted in the Biblical Dominion Mandate  

*(Imagined as a thoughtful, principled exchange—Scully’s signature style—after reviewing the framework. He’d speak with the calm, moral clarity of a journalist and speechwriter who has walked the killing floors of slaughterhouses and the decks of whaling ships, believing that **true dominion is not domination but merciful stewardship**, and that our treatment of the vulnerable—animal or human—reveals the state of our souls.)*  

